We are looking for a Senior Software Developer with 6+ years of experience in building scalable web applications and microservices. The ideal candidate is proficient in Node.js, Nest.js, React, TypeScript, and cloud technologies including AWS, Docker, and Kubernetes.

Responsibilities

Develop and optimize microservices using Node.js/Nest.js and Kafka for high-scale applications.

Improve system performance through database indexing, caching (Redis), and API optimization.

Implement CI/CD pipelines using GitHub Actions, Docker, and Kubernetes for efficient deployments.

Build secure authentication systems using OAuth 2.0, JWT, and follow OWASP best practices.

Collaborate with cross-functional teams using Agile workflows, contributing to frontend development with React and Next.js.

Maintain code quality through standards, documentation, and mentoring junior developers.

Required Skills

Node.js, Nest.js, Express.js

React, Next.js, Redux

MongoDB, MySQL, Redis

Kafka, Socket.io

AWS, Docker, Kubernetes, CI/CD

Jest, Swagger, Git/GitHub




